▶ {HoSHal ghajchugh vay', mI' naghmey tIronmoH. wa'maHlogh boq'egh mI' naghmey; chen qav'ap. ghajwI'vaD qav'ap yIDIl.:sen:nolink} "If [energy source is] owned, throw dice and pay owner a total ten times amount shown."[2]

There are five types of noun suffixes in Klingon.

Noun Type 1: Augmentative/diminutive
▶ {-'a':n:suff}
▶ {-Hom:n:suff}
▶ {-oy:n:suff}

Noun Type 2: Number
▶ {-pu':n:suff}
▶ {-Du':n:suff}
▶ {-mey:n:suff}

Noun Type 3: Qualification
▶ {-qoq:n:suff}
▶ {-Hey:n:suff}
▶ {-na':n:suff}

Noun Type 4: Possession/specification
▶ {-wIj:n:suff} / {-wI':n:suff}
▶ {-lIj:n:suff} / {-lI':n:suff}
▶ {-Daj:n:suff}
▶ {-maj:n:suff} / {-ma':n:suff}
▶ {-raj:n:suff} / {-ra':n:suff}
▶ {-chaj:n:suff}
▶ {-vam:n:suff}
▶ {-vetlh:n:suff}

Noun Type 5: Syntactic markers
▶ {-Daq:n:suff}
▶ {-vo':n:suff}
▶ {-mo':n:suff}
▶ {-vaD:n:suff}
▶ {-'e':n:suff}

Есть пять типов суффиксов для имен существительных в Клингонском языке.

Тип 1: Усиливающий/уменьшающий
▶ {-'a':n:suff}
▶ {-Hom:n:suff}
▶ {-oy:n:suff}

Тип 2: Числительные
▶ {-pu':n:suff}
▶ {-Du':n:suff}
▶ {-mey:n:suff}

Тип 3: Квалифицирующие
▶ {-qoq:n:suff}
▶ {-Hey:n:suff}
▶ {-na':n:suff}

Тип 4: имущественные/определяющие
▶ {-wIj:n:suff} / {-wI':n:suff}
▶ {-lIj:n:suff} / {-lI':n:suff}
▶ {-Daj:n:suff}
▶ {-maj:n:suff} / {-ma':n:suff}
▶ {-raj:n:suff} / {-ra':n:suff}
▶ {-chaj:n:suff}
▶ {-vam:n:suff}
▶ {-vetlh:n:suff}

Тип 5: Синтаксические маркеры
▶ {-Daq:n:suff}
▶ {-vo':n:suff}
▶ {-mo':n:suff}
▶ {-vaD:n:suff}
▶ {-'e':n:suff}

